Zero.

00:18:20.810 --> 00:18:21.670
OK.

00:18:21.670 --> 00:18:23.080
That's the conclusion.

00:18:23.080 --> 00:18:25.390
Those have to be the same.

00:18:25.390 --> 00:18:28.460
dv_2/dx - dv_1/dy
has to be zero.

00:18:28.460 --> 00:18:31.990
OK.

00:18:31.990 --> 00:18:35.420
Because those are the same.

