00:39:21.970 --> 00:39:24.300
So we now have a test.

00:39:24.300 --> 00:39:28.070
We now have a test.

00:39:28.070 --> 00:39:32.840
This is our test, right?

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:34.320
That's our test.

00:39:34.320 --> 00:39:41.190
But I have to connect it
